    </div>

    <p>This guide is part of our <a href="/candy/">candy hub</a>, which also covers <a href="/candy/vegan-gummy-bears/">vegan gummy bears</a>, <a href="/candy/vegan-sour-gummies/">vegan sour gummies</a>, and <a href="/sugar-free-gummies/">sugar-free gummies</a> across all categories. If you are specifically looking for plant-based sour options, our dedicated <a href="/candy/vegan-sour-gummies/">vegan sour gummies</a> guide covers that niche in depth.</p>

