    <h3>Why SmartSweets Sour Blast Buddies Are the Best Low-Sugar Sour Gummy</h3>

    <p>SmartSweets Sour Blast Buddies are the clear winner for anyone who wants a genuine sour candy experience without the sugar crash. At 3 grams of sugar per bag — compared to 24 grams in a comparable serving of Sour Patch Kids — they deliver an 87% sugar reduction without eliminating the sour satisfaction that makes sour candy worth eating. The secret is a dual-acid coating system: citric acid provides the initial sharp hit, while malic acid extends the sour flavor through the chew. The allulose-stevia sweetener blend creates a clean sweetness that never tastes artificial or metallic, which is a common failure point in sugar-free candy.</p>

    <p>In our blind taste panel, SmartSweets Sour Blast Buddies ranked second in "sour satisfaction" behind only Sour Patch Kids — remarkable for a product with 87% less sugar. The fun character shapes (aliens, robots, and spaceships) add a visual element that makes them appealing for kids and adults who want a playful candy experience. For anyone managing blood sugar, counting calories, or simply reducing sugar intake without giving up sour candy entirely, Sour Blast Buddies are the definitive choice. They are widely available at Target, Walmart, Whole Foods, Amazon, and most grocery chains. See also our <a href="/sugar-free-gummies/">sugar-free gummies</a> guide for more low-sugar options across all candy and supplement categories.</p>

